name: Buntu Lane
address: Br Gata, Buahan Kaja, Kec. Payangan, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80572, Indonesia
review 1: Pristine, beautiful, old Bali. Incredible nature walks along the river and one of the most friendly villages I've experienced in Bali. Unbelievable views!
review 2: The best John Hardy Experience ever! Bike, Hike, and soon Sleep in an amazing part of Bali that is largely undiscovered by travelers
review 3:
This place is so beautiful!
The views of the mountains and rice fields  are breathtakingly stunning.
